cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator model to an invalid value 'invalid_model' will cause RF simulation initialization errors and prevent proper system startup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器模型設定為無效值 'invalid_model' 會導致 RF 模擬初始化錯誤，並阻止系統正確啟動。
